Thread on Atmospheric beasts:

These are some of the most interesting and elusive creatures, rumored to roam our world. Breaking all known laws of nature, they seem to be composed of semi-solid matter with incredibly low density - basically a living, organic cloud.

In the field of UFOlogy, the strangest reports concern sightings of very unusually shaped flying objects that do not look like machinery of any sort, but a living, biological creature.

Some have proposed that at very high altitudes there exists a whole hidden low-density fauna.

Some researchers claim that these creatures are able to change their shape - and even shrink or greatly expand (while lowering their density tremendously). Another feature is the ability to squirt water.

Witnesses tell that cloud beasts greatly resemble weird deep sea creatures.
